```text
CurrentHolderActor
PreviousHolderActor
RemainingTime
IsActive
IsSummitFinal
RoundNumber
StateVersion
```

## 필수 로그

```text
[PTB][BombStateData][CREATED]
[PTB][BombStateData][HOLDER_CHANGED]
[PTB][BombStateData][VERSION_CHANGED]
[PTB][BombStateData][INVALID_TRANSITION]
[PTB][BombStateData][SELF_TEST_PASS]
