```text
HolderActorNumber
IsBuffActive
OriginalMoveMultiplier
OriginalClimbMultiplier
HadInfiniteStaminaBeforeBomb
AppliedBombStateVersion
```

## 필수 로그

```text
[PTB][BuffState][CAPTURED]
[PTB][BuffState][VERSION_SET]
[PTB][BuffState][RESET]
[PTB][BuffState][INVALID_STATE]
[PTB][BuffState][SELF_TEST_PASS]
